1
00:00:09,218 --> 00:00:11,302
<font color="yellow"><i>Ibu!</i></font>

2
00:00:11,470 --> 00:00:13,388
<font color="yellow"><i>Ibu di sini.</i></font>

3
00:00:26,568 --> 00:00:28,194
<font color="yellow">Ada hasil?</font>

4
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:31,823
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana kita tahu
jika itu beracun?</font>

5
00:00:32,866 --> 00:00:36,327
<font color="yellow">Hanya ada satu cara pasti
yang kuketahui.</font>

6
00:00:38,539 --> 00:00:40,248
<font color="yellow">Tanya pada Shane
saat dia kembali?</font>

7
00:00:40,416 --> 00:00:41,916
<font color="yellow">Ya, kau benar.</font>

8
00:00:42,084 --> 00:00:43,418
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

9
00:00:46,046 --> 00:00:48,464
<font color="yellow">Dale, aku akan keluar.</font>

10
00:00:48,632 --> 00:00:51,342
<font color="yellow">Sayang, Ibu ingin kau ada
di tempat Dale bisa melihatmu.</font>

11
00:00:51,510 --> 00:00:53,094
<font color="yellow">Baik, Bu.</font>

12
00:00:53,262 --> 00:00:55,346
<font color="yellow">Kau juga.
Jangan berkeliaran terlalu jauh.</font>

13
00:00:55,514 --> 00:00:56,931
<font color="yellow">Tetaplah berada di sekitar sini.</font>

14
00:00:57,099 --> 00:00:59,767
<font color="yellow">Jika kau lihat sesuatu, berteriaklah.
Aku akan datang.</font>

15
00:00:59,935 --> 00:01:01,811
<font color="yellow">Ya, Bu.</font>

16
00:02:41,370 --> 00:02:43,204
<font color="yellow">Kau membuatku sangat ketakutan.</font>

17
00:02:43,372 --> 00:02:45,498
<font color="yellow">Aku yakin begitu. Itu yang kau
dapat karena membuatku menunggu.</font>

18
00:02:45,666 --> 00:02:46,999
<font color="yellow">Aku mencoba tenang.</font>

19
00:02:47,167 --> 00:02:49,210
<font color="yellow">- Kau dari mana?
- Amy si ratu jamur...</font>

20
00:02:49,378 --> 00:02:51,504
<font color="yellow">...aku harus menunggu dia
kembali.</font>

21
00:02:57,636 --> 00:02:59,846
<font color="yellow">- Berapa banyak waktu kita?
- Cukup.</font>

22
00:03:53,692 --> 00:03:55,568
<font color="yellow">- Kemarilah.
- Baiklah.</font>

23
00:04:04,233 --> 00:04:34,169
<font color="yellow">--- Penerjemah: Rizal Adam ---
http://rizaladam.wordpress.com</font>

24
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:39,701
<font color="yellow">SEASON 1 EPISODE 2
GUTS</font>

25
00:04:59,675 --> 00:05:01,092
<font color="yellow"><i>Hei, kau masih hidup
di dalam sana?</i></font>

26
00:05:03,971 --> 00:05:06,597
<font color="yellow">- Halo?
- Rupanya kau masih hidup.</font>

27
00:05:06,765 --> 00:05:08,349
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau membuatku bertanya-tanya.</i></font>

28
00:05:08,517 --> 00:05:09,934
<font color="yellow">Kau di mana? Di luar?</font>

29
00:05:10,102 --> 00:05:11,560
<font color="yellow">Kau bisa melihatku sekarang?</font>

30
00:05:11,728 --> 00:05:13,771
<font color="yellow"><i>Ya, aku bisa melihatmu.</i></font>

31
00:05:13,939 --> 00:05:16,565
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau dikelilingi zombie.
Itu kabar buruknya.</i></font>

32
00:05:16,733 --> 00:05:18,484
<font color="yellow">Ada kabar baiknya?</font>

33
00:05:18,652 --> 00:05:21,320
<font color="yellow">- Tidak.
- Dengar, siapa pun kau...</font>

34
00:05:21,488 --> 00:05:23,948
<font color="yellow">...aku tak keberatan memberitahu
aku agak prihatin di sini.</font>

35
00:05:24,116 --> 00:05:27,576
<font color="yellow"><i>Bung, kau harus melihatnya
dari atas sini.</i></font>

36
00:05:27,744 --> 00:05:30,121
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau akan sangat ketakutan.</i></font>

37
00:05:30,288 --> 00:05:32,623
<font color="yellow">Ada saran untukku?</font>

38
00:05:32,791 --> 00:05:36,127
<font color="yellow"><i>Ya, larilah menyelamatkan diri.</i></font>

39
00:05:38,046 --> 00:05:40,131
<font color="yellow">Hanya itu?
"Lari menyelamatkan diri"?</font>

40
00:05:40,298 --> 00:05:41,841
<font color="yellow"><i>Caraku tak seburuk yang
terdengar.</i></font>

41
00:05:42,009 --> 00:05:43,884
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau memiliki pandangan
dari luar sini.</i></font>

42
00:05:44,052 --> 00:05:46,512
<font color="yellow"><i>Masih ada satu orang di atas tank
namun yang lainnya telah turun...</i></font>

43
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,806
<font color="yellow"><i>...dan bergabung di pesta tempat
kuda itu mati.</i></font>

44
00:05:48,974 --> 00:05:50,683
<font color="yellow">- Kau masih mendengarkanku?
- Sejauh ini.</font>

45
00:05:50,851 --> 00:05:53,477
<font color="yellow"><i>Baik, jalan di sisi lain tank
tak terlalu ramai.</i></font>

46
00:05:53,645 --> 00:05:56,063
<font color="yellow"><i>Jika kau bergerak selagi mereka
teralihkan, kau punya peluang.</i></font>

47
00:05:56,231 --> 00:05:58,232
<font color="yellow">- Kau punya amunisi?
- Di dalam tas besar...</font>

48
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,400
<font color="yellow">...yang kujatuhkan di luar sana,
serta senjata. Bisa aku meraihnya?</font>

49
00:06:00,527 --> 00:06:02,862
<font color="yellow"><i>Lupakan tas itu.
Itu bukan pilihan.</i></font>

50
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:05,364
<font color="yellow">- Apa yang kau miliki?
- Tunggu.</font>

51
00:06:23,175 --> 00:06:26,302
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

52
00:06:26,470 --> 00:06:28,971
<font color="yellow">Aku punya pistol Beretta
dengan satu magasin...</font>

53
00:06:29,139 --> 00:06:31,891
<font color="yellow">- ...15 peluru.
- Manfaatkan dengan baik.</font>

54
00:06:32,059 --> 00:06:34,685
<font color="yellow">Lompatlah ke sisi kanan tank,
terus berjalan ke arah situ.</font>

55
00:06:34,853 --> 00:06:37,229
<font color="yellow">Ada sebuang gang di ujung jalan,
mungkin jaraknya 45 meter.</font>

56
00:06:37,397 --> 00:06:39,148
<font color="yellow">Datanglah ke sana.</font>

57
00:06:39,316 --> 00:06:41,317
<font color="yellow">Hei, siapa namamu?</font>

58
00:06:41,485 --> 00:06:44,153
<font color="yellow">Kau mendengarkanku?
Kau kehabisan waktu.</font>

59
00:06:44,321 --> 00:06:45,571
<font color="yellow">Benar.</font>

60
00:07:16,311 --> 00:07:17,853
<font color="yellow">Belum mati!</font>

61
00:07:18,021 --> 00:07:19,396
<font color="yellow">Ayo!</font>

62
00:07:19,564 --> 00:07:21,315
<font color="yellow">Di belakang sini!</font>

63
00:07:22,359 --> 00:07:24,985
<font color="yellow">Ayo!</font>

64
00:07:30,283 --> 00:07:32,284
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau lakukan?
Ayo!</font>

65
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:45,297
<font color="yellow">Ayo, naiklah.</font>

66
00:07:56,476 --> 00:07:58,644
<font color="yellow">Gerakan yang hebat,
Clint Eastwood.</font>

67
00:07:58,812 --> 00:08:01,939
<font color="yellow">Kau sheriff yang baru datang
untuk membersihkan kota?</font>

68
00:08:02,107 --> 00:08:05,151
<font color="yellow">- Bukan itu niatku.
- Ya, terserahlah.</font>

69
00:08:05,318 --> 00:08:07,945
<font color="yellow">Kau tetaplah orang
yang bodoh.</font>

70
00:08:08,113 --> 00:08:10,823
<font color="yellow">Rick. Terima kasih.</font>

71
00:08:11,867 --> 00:08:14,160
<font color="yellow">Glenn. Sama-sama.</font>

72
00:08:15,662 --> 00:08:16,829
<font color="yellow">Celaka.</font>

73
00:08:24,462 --> 00:08:26,005
<font color="yellow">Sisi positifnya...</font>

74
00:08:26,173 --> 00:08:28,174
<font color="yellow">...kita akan tewas karena jatuh.</font>

75
00:08:28,341 --> 00:08:30,885
<font color="yellow">Aku pria yang selalu optimis.</font>

76
00:08:37,267 --> 00:08:39,143
<font color="yellow">Apa kau yang merintangi
gang itu?</font>

77
00:08:39,311 --> 00:08:42,354
<font color="yellow">Seseorang melakukannya. Kurasa
saat kota ini diambil alih.</font>

78
00:08:42,522 --> 00:08:45,232
<font color="yellow">Siapa pun yang melakukannya mengira
tak banyak zombie bisa menerobosnya.</font>

79
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,401
<font color="yellow">Di tank itu, kenapa kau
pertaruhkan nyawamu untukku?</font>

80
00:08:47,569 --> 00:08:49,778
<font color="yellow">Anggap itu harapan
naif yang bodoh...</font>

81
00:08:49,946 --> 00:08:52,072
<font color="yellow">...bahwa jika aku berbuat
sejauh itu...</font>

82
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,616
<font color="yellow">....seseorang mungkin akan
melakukan hal yang sama untukku.</font>

83
00:08:53,783 --> 00:08:56,368
<font color="yellow">Kurasa aku bahkan lebih
bodoh daripada kau.</font>

84
00:09:14,095 --> 00:09:16,347
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah kembali. Ada satu tamu
ditambah 4 zombie di gang.</font>

85
00:09:32,489 --> 00:09:33,593
<font color="yellow">Ayo!</font>

86
00:09:36,326 --> 00:09:37,785
<font color="yellow">Morales, ayo!</font>

87
00:09:41,081 --> 00:09:42,748
<font color="yellow">Dasar bajingan.
Kami harus membunuhmu.</font>

88
00:09:42,916 --> 00:09:45,876
<font color="yellow">- Tenang saja, Andrea. Mundurlah.
- Ayo, tenanglah.</font>

89
00:09:46,044 --> 00:09:47,378
<font color="yellow">Tenang?
Kau bergurau, 'kan?</font>

90
00:09:47,545 --> 00:09:49,713
<font color="yellow">Kita akan mati gara-gara
orang bodoh ini.</font>

91
00:09:49,881 --> 00:09:53,509
<font color="yellow">Andrea, kubilang mundur.</font>

92
00:09:59,766 --> 00:10:01,058
<font color="yellow">Atau tarik saja pelatuknya.</font>

93
00:10:04,479 --> 00:10:06,855
<font color="yellow">Matilah kita semua...</font>

94
00:10:07,941 --> 00:10:09,775
<font color="yellow">...gara-gara kau.</font>

95
00:10:11,611 --> 00:10:14,029
<font color="yellow">Aku tak paham.</font>

96
00:10:14,197 --> 00:10:17,116
<font color="yellow">Dengar, kami datang ke kota
untuk mencari persediaan.</font>

97
00:10:17,284 --> 00:10:19,368
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu apa kunci mencari
persediaan? Bertahan hidup!</font>

98
00:10:19,536 --> 00:10:22,329
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu kunci bertahan hidup?
Mengendap-endap, menyelinap.</font>

99
00:10:22,497 --> 00:10:24,456
<font color="yellow">Bukannya menembak di jalan
seperti sedang berpesta.</font>

100
00:10:24,624 --> 00:10:27,167
<font color="yellow">Setiap zombie bermil-mil jauhnya
mendengar suara tembakanmu.</font>

101
00:10:27,335 --> 00:10:29,420
<font color="yellow">Kau baru saja membunyikan
bel makan malam.</font>

102
00:10:29,587 --> 00:10:31,422
<font color="yellow">Kau paham sekarang?</font>

103
00:10:38,471 --> 00:10:40,472
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan.</font>

104
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:47,980
<font color="yellow">Sedang apa kau di luar sana?</font>

105
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:49,481
<font color="yellow">Mencoba mengejar helikopter.</font>

106
00:10:49,649 --> 00:10:51,400
<font color="yellow">Helikopter?
Bung, itu omong kosong.</font>

107
00:10:51,568 --> 00:10:53,110
<font color="yellow">- Tak ada helikopter.
- Kau mengejar...</font>

108
00:10:53,278 --> 00:10:54,653
<font color="yellow">...halusinasi, berkhayal.
Itu sering terjadi.</font>

109
00:10:54,821 --> 00:10:56,155
<font color="yellow">Aku melihatnya.</font>

110
00:10:57,657 --> 00:11:00,117
<font color="yellow">T-Dog, coba radio itu.
Kau bisa hubungi yang lainnya?</font>

111
00:11:00,285 --> 00:11:02,369
<font color="yellow">Yang lainnya?
Pusat pengungsi?</font>

112
00:11:02,537 --> 00:11:05,289
<font color="yellow">Ya, pusat pengungsi. Mereka akan
menyiapkan biskuit hangat untuk kita.</font>

113
00:11:05,457 --> 00:11:08,542
<font color="yellow">Tak ada sinyal.
Mungkin atapnya.</font>

114
00:11:10,894 --> 00:11:12,046
<font color="yellow">Tidak. Apakah itu Dixon?</font>

115
00:11:12,213 --> 00:11:14,673
<font color="yellow">- Apa yang dilakukan orang gila itu?
- Ayo, mari pergi.</font>

116
00:11:31,733 --> 00:11:33,646
<font color="yellow">Dixon, apa kau sudah gila?</font>

117
00:11:36,393 --> 00:11:37,988
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

118
00:11:38,156 --> 00:11:41,867
<font color="yellow">Kalian bersikap sopanlah
dengan pria bersenjata!</font>

119
00:11:44,537 --> 00:11:46,205
<font color="yellow">Hanya kepekaan biasa.</font>

120
00:11:46,373 --> 00:11:48,707
<font color="yellow">Kau buang-buang peluru yang
bahkan kita tak punya!</font>

121
00:11:48,875 --> 00:11:51,377
<font color="yellow">Dan kau mengundang lebih banyak
dari mereka! Tenanglah, Bung.</font>

122
00:11:51,544 --> 00:11:54,046
<font color="yellow">Sudah cukup buruk seharian
aku diikuti si bodoh ini.</font>

123
00:11:54,214 --> 00:11:56,048
<font color="yellow">Kini aku harus mendengarkanmu?</font>

124
00:11:56,216 --> 00:11:59,259
<font color="yellow">Kurasa tidak, Kawan.
Masanya sudah lewat.</font>

125
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:01,261
<font color="yellow">"Masanya sudah lewat"?
Kau ada sesuatu...</font>

126
00:12:01,429 --> 00:12:03,639
<font color="yellow">- ...yang ingin kau sampaikan?
- T-Dog, biarkan saja.</font>

127
00:12:03,807 --> 00:12:05,182
<font color="yellow">- Tidak.
- Ini tak setimpal.</font>

128
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:08,352
<font color="yellow">Merle, tenang saja.</font>

129
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,354
<font color="yellow">Kita sudah memiliki cukup
banyak masalah.</font>

130
00:12:10,522 --> 00:12:12,856
<font color="yellow">- Kau mau tahu saatnya?
- Ya.</font>

131
00:12:13,024 --> 00:12:16,652
<font color="yellow">Kuberitahu saatnya, Tn. "Asyik."
Ini saatnya aku menerima perintah...</font>

132
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:18,035
<font color="yellow">...dari seorang negro.</font>

133
00:12:18,154 --> 00:12:19,947
<font color="yellow">Ayolah, Merle.
Sudah cukup.</font>

134
00:12:20,115 --> 00:12:21,179
<font color="yellow">Ayolah.</font>

135
00:12:21,866 --> 00:12:23,909
<font color="yellow">Dixon!</font>

136
00:12:24,077 --> 00:12:25,411
<font color="yellow">Hentikan!</font>

137
00:12:25,578 --> 00:12:28,705
<font color="yellow">Hentikan!
Dixon, ayolah! Menyingkir darinya!</font>

138
00:12:28,873 --> 00:12:30,165
<font color="yellow">Dixon, kau akan melukainya.</font>

139
00:12:33,461 --> 00:12:35,879
<font color="yellow">Merle, hentikan!</font>

140
00:12:44,055 --> 00:12:46,140
<font color="yellow">Jangan, kumohon.</font>

141
00:13:04,409 --> 00:13:07,202
<font color="yellow">Ya! Baiklah!</font>

142
00:13:07,370 --> 00:13:10,581
<font color="yellow">Kita akan lakukan
sedikit pemilihan suara.</font>

143
00:13:10,748 --> 00:13:14,209
<font color="yellow">Bicara soal siapa yang
memimpin.</font>

144
00:13:14,377 --> 00:13:17,129
<font color="yellow">Aku memilih diriku.
Ada yang lain?</font>

145
00:13:17,297 --> 00:13:20,132
<font color="yellow">Saatnya demokrasi, semuanya.</font>

146
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:22,634
<font color="yellow">Angkatlah tangan kalian.</font>

147
00:13:22,802 --> 00:13:25,512
<font color="yellow">Semua setuju?</font>

148
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:28,056
<font color="yellow">Ayolah.
Biar kulihat.</font>

149
00:13:28,224 --> 00:13:29,266
<font color="yellow">Yang benar saja.</font>

150
00:13:29,434 --> 00:13:31,143
<font color="yellow">Semuanya setuju?</font>

151
00:13:31,311 --> 00:13:34,646
<font color="yellow">Ya. Itu bagus.</font>

152
00:13:34,814 --> 00:13:38,108
<font color="yellow">Itu artinya aku pemimpinnya,
bukan?</font>

153
00:13:38,276 --> 00:13:41,487
<font color="yellow">Bagus.
Ada yang lain lagi?</font>

154
00:13:41,654 --> 00:13:44,448
<font color="yellow">- Ada lagi?
- Ya.</font>

155
00:13:55,168 --> 00:13:57,836
<font color="yellow">- Siapa kau?
- Polisi yang ramah.</font>

156
00:14:00,256 --> 00:14:03,175
<font color="yellow">Dengarlah ini, Merle.
Situasinya kini berbeda.</font>

157
00:14:03,343 --> 00:14:06,261
<font color="yellow">Tak ada negro lagi.</font>

158
00:14:06,429 --> 00:14:09,389
<font color="yellow">Juga tak ada gelandangan
bodoh berkulit putih.</font>

159
00:14:09,557 --> 00:14:12,017
<font color="yellow">Hanya daging gelap
dan daging putih.</font>

160
00:14:12,185 --> 00:14:13,852
<font color="yellow">Hanya kita dan para zombie.</font>

161
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:15,812
<font color="yellow">Kita bisa bertahan dengan bersatu...</font>

162
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:18,690
<font color="yellow">- ...bukan berpecah.
- Persetan denganmu, Bung.</font>

163
00:14:20,193 --> 00:14:22,569
<font color="yellow">Bisa kulihat kau tak
mengerti maksudnya.</font>

164
00:14:22,737 --> 00:14:25,072
<font color="yellow">Benarkah? Kalau begitu,
persetan dua kali denganmu.</font>

165
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,282
<font color="yellow">Bersikap sopanlah dengan
pria bersenjata.</font>

166
00:14:27,450 --> 00:14:29,159
<font color="yellow">Hanya kepekaan biasa.</font>

167
00:14:31,871 --> 00:14:34,540
<font color="yellow">Kau takkan berani.
Kau seorang polisi.</font>

168
00:14:36,167 --> 00:14:40,045
<font color="yellow">Aku kini hanya seorang pria
yang mencari istri dan putranya.</font>

169
00:14:40,213 --> 00:14:43,298
<font color="yellow">Siapa pun yang merintangi,
dia akan kalah.</font>

170
00:14:45,176 --> 00:14:47,719
<font color="yellow">Akan kuberi kau waktu
untuk memikirkan itu.</font>

171
00:14:58,231 --> 00:15:00,232
<font color="yellow">Ada sedikit sisanya
di hidungmu.</font>

172
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:02,526
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan kau lakukan?</font>

173
00:15:02,694 --> 00:15:04,152
<font color="yellow">Menangkapku?</font>

174
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:07,155
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan kau lakukan?
Itu barangku!</font>

175
00:15:07,323 --> 00:15:09,408
<font color="yellow">Hei!</font>

176
00:15:09,576 --> 00:15:11,493
<font color="yellow">Jika aku bisa lepas,
sebaiknya kau berdoa.</font>

177
00:15:11,661 --> 00:15:14,371
<font color="yellow">Kau dengar aku, Bajingan?</font>

178
00:15:14,539 --> 00:15:16,373
<font color="yellow">- Kau dengar aku?
- Ya, suaramu cukup keras.</font>

179
00:15:16,541 --> 00:15:18,625
<font color="yellow">Kau dengar aku, Brengsek?</font>

180
00:15:20,587 --> 00:15:23,338
<font color="yellow">Kau bukan anggota
Kepolisian Atlanta.</font>

181
00:15:24,549 --> 00:15:27,926
<font color="yellow">- Dari mana asalmu?
- Dari sebuah tempat.</font>

182
00:15:28,094 --> 00:15:32,764
<font color="yellow">Petugas yang ramah dari
sebuah tempat.</font>

183
00:15:32,932 --> 00:15:35,292
<font color="yellow">Selamat datang di kota besar.</font>

184
00:15:46,863 --> 00:15:48,947
<font color="yellow">Astaga, di bawah sana
seperti Times Square.</font>

185
00:15:49,115 --> 00:15:53,285
<font color="yellow">- Bagaimana sinyalnya?
- Seperti otak Dixon. Lemah.</font>

186
00:15:54,954 --> 00:15:56,079
<font color="yellow">Teruslah mencoba.</font>

187
00:15:56,247 --> 00:15:57,706
<font color="yellow">Kenapa?
Tak ada yang bisa mereka lakukan.</font>

188
00:15:57,874 --> 00:15:59,333
<font color="yellow">Tak satu tindakan pun.</font>

189
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:01,793
<font color="yellow">Hanya ada beberapa orang
di luar kota.</font>

190
00:16:01,961 --> 00:16:04,171
<font color="yellow">Tak ada pusat pengungsi.
Itu hanya khayalan.</font>

191
00:16:04,339 --> 00:16:06,173
<font color="yellow">Maka dia benar.
Kita sendirian.</font>

192
00:16:06,341 --> 00:16:07,507
<font color="yellow">Terserah kita untuk bisa keluar.</font>

193
00:16:07,675 --> 00:16:09,051
<font color="yellow">Semoga berhasil dengan itu.</font>

194
00:16:09,218 --> 00:16:11,970
<font color="yellow">Kudengar jalan-jalan di wilayah
ini tidak aman.</font>

195
00:16:12,138 --> 00:16:15,182
<font color="yellow">Bukankah itu benar, Manis?</font>

196
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:17,476
<font color="yellow">Hei, Sayang.</font>

197
00:16:17,644 --> 00:16:19,269
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana jika kau melepaskanku
dari borgol ini...</font>

198
00:16:19,437 --> 00:16:22,522
<font color="yellow">...kita pergi ke suatu tempat
dan membunuh beberapa zombie?</font>

199
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:26,151
<font color="yellow">- Kita akan tetap mati.
- Lebih baik begitu.</font>

200
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:30,822
<font color="yellow">Pengunyah karpet.
Kupikir begitu.</font>

201
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:32,908
<font color="yellow">"Jalan-jalan tidak aman."</font>

202
00:16:33,076 --> 00:16:34,660
<font color="yellow">Itu meremehkan.</font>

203
00:16:34,827 --> 00:16:37,496
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana dengan di bawah
jalan? Gorong-gorong?</font>

204
00:16:37,664 --> 00:16:39,581
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

205
00:16:39,749 --> 00:16:41,667
<font color="yellow">Glenn, periksa gangnya.</font>

206
00:16:41,834 --> 00:16:43,502
<font color="yellow">Kau lihat ada penutup
gorong-gorong?</font>

207
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:55,347
<font color="yellow">Tidak, pasti ada di jalan
tempat para zombie itu berada.</font>

208
00:16:55,515 --> 00:16:58,558
<font color="yellow">Mungkin tidak. Gedung tua
seperti ini dibangun tahun 20-an.</font>

209
00:16:58,726 --> 00:17:01,520
<font color="yellow">Gedung besar sering memiliki
terowongan drainase menuju selokan...</font>

210
00:17:01,688 --> 00:17:03,939
<font color="yellow">...jika terjadi banjir
di ruang bawah tanah.</font>

211
00:17:04,107 --> 00:17:06,692
<font color="yellow">- Bagaimana kau tahu itu?
- Itu pekerjaanku, dulunya.</font>

212
00:17:06,859 --> 00:17:08,568
<font color="yellow">Aku bekerja di kantor
penataan kota.</font>

213
00:17:20,832 --> 00:17:22,874
<font color="yellow">Ini dia?
Kau yakin?</font>

214
00:17:23,042 --> 00:17:25,836
<font color="yellow">Aku benar-benar periksa tempat
ini terakhir kali kemari.</font>

215
00:17:26,003 --> 00:17:28,046
<font color="yellow">Ini satu-satunya tempat
di sini yang mengarah ke bawah.</font>

216
00:17:29,215 --> 00:17:30,590
<font color="yellow">Tapi aku tak pernah turun.</font>

217
00:17:30,758 --> 00:17:33,218
<font color="yellow">Siapa yang mau?</font>

218
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:40,559
<font color="yellow">Bagus.</font>

219
00:17:42,145 --> 00:17:44,438
<font color="yellow">- Kami akan di belakangmu.
- Tidak. Jangan kau.</font>

220
00:17:44,605 --> 00:17:46,648
<font color="yellow">Kenapa tidak?
Kau pikir aku tak bisa?</font>

221
00:17:46,816 --> 00:17:48,650
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak...</font>

222
00:17:48,818 --> 00:17:50,402
<font color="yellow">Utarakan pendapatmu.</font>

223
00:17:52,321 --> 00:17:56,450
<font color="yellow">Dengar, sampai sekarang aku
selalu datang kemari sendirian...</font>

224
00:17:56,617 --> 00:17:59,077
<font color="yellow">...keluar masuk mengambil beberapa
benda. Bukan masalah.</font>

225
00:17:59,245 --> 00:18:01,747
<font color="yellow">Saat pertama aku mengajak
kelompok, semuanya berantakan.</font>

226
00:18:01,914 --> 00:18:03,707
<font color="yellow">Jangan tersinggung.</font>

227
00:18:05,752 --> 00:18:08,378
<font color="yellow">Jika kau ingin aku menuruni
lubang ini, tak apa.</font>

228
00:18:09,422 --> 00:18:11,673
<font color="yellow">Tapi jika kita melakukannya
dengan caraku.</font>

229
00:18:11,841 --> 00:18:14,593
<font color="yellow">Di bawah sana sempit. Jika aku
temui sesuatu dan harus keluar cepat...</font>

230
00:18:14,761 --> 00:18:16,928
<font color="yellow">...aku tak mau kalian tersendat
di belakangku, membuatku terbunuh.</font>

231
00:18:18,139 --> 00:18:21,433
<font color="yellow">Akan kupilih satu orang.
Kau juga bukan.</font>

232
00:18:21,601 --> 00:18:23,810
<font color="yellow">Kau memiliki senjata Merle
dan aku melihatmu menembak.</font>

233
00:18:23,978 --> 00:18:25,729
<font color="yellow">Aku akan merasa lebih baik
jika kau di luar toko...</font>

234
00:18:25,897 --> 00:18:27,939
<font color="yellow">...mengawasi pintu untuk
menjaga kami.</font>

235
00:18:28,107 --> 00:18:30,275
<font color="yellow">Kau juga membawa senjata,
jadi kau harus ikut dengannya.</font>

236
00:18:30,443 --> 00:18:33,403
<font color="yellow">Kau menjadi pendampingku.
Jacqui tetap di sini.</font>

237
00:18:33,571 --> 00:18:35,447
<font color="yellow">Jika sesuatu terjadi,
berteriaklah...</font>

238
00:18:35,615 --> 00:18:37,032
<font color="yellow">- ...agar kami segera ke sini.
- Baiklah.</font>

239
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:40,285
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, semuanya sudah
tahu tugas masing-masing.</font>

240
00:19:47,228 --> 00:19:49,229
<font color="yellow">Maaf sudah menodongkan
pistol ke wajahmu.</font>

241
00:19:50,481 --> 00:19:52,649
<font color="yellow">Orang-orang berbuat apa
saja saat ketakutan.</font>

242
00:19:52,817 --> 00:19:54,985
<font color="yellow">Bukannya itu benar-benar
tak sengaja.</font>

243
00:19:55,152 --> 00:19:57,863
<font color="yellow">Kau memang menyebabkan
kami terlibat ini semua.</font>

244
00:19:58,030 --> 00:20:00,031
<font color="yellow">Jika aku mengeluarkan kita semua,
akankah cukup untuk menebusnya?</font>

245
00:20:00,199 --> 00:20:03,577
<font color="yellow">Tidak. Tapi itu akan
menjadi permulaan.</font>

246
00:20:15,882 --> 00:20:18,383
<font color="yellow">Namun lain kali,
lepaskan pengamannya.</font>

247
00:20:18,551 --> 00:20:20,051
<font color="yellow">Atau senjata itu tak
bisa dipakai.</font>

248
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,306
<font color="yellow">Itu senjatamu?</font>

249
00:20:24,473 --> 00:20:26,433
<font color="yellow">Ini hadiah.
Kenapa?</font>

250
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:32,814
<font color="yellow">Titik merah kecil artinya
siap ditembakkan.</font>

251
00:20:32,982 --> 00:20:35,317
<font color="yellow">Kau mungkin harus memakainya.</font>

252
00:20:38,112 --> 00:20:40,071
<font color="yellow">Senang mengetahuinya.</font>

253
00:20:42,909 --> 00:20:45,733
<font color="yellow">Ada orang di luar sana?</font>

254
00:20:48,581 --> 00:20:51,207
<font color="yellow">Halo? Ada yang mendengar?</font>

255
00:20:51,375 --> 00:20:52,709
<font color="yellow">Aku berharap mendengar
suara seseorang...</font>

256
00:20:52,877 --> 00:20:54,586
<font color="yellow">...karena aku sudah muak
mendengar suaraku sendiri.</font>

257
00:20:54,754 --> 00:20:57,047
<font color="yellow">Ya, itu berarti kita berdua.</font>

258
00:20:57,214 --> 00:20:59,090
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau tak matikan itu?</font>

259
00:20:59,258 --> 00:21:00,800
<font color="yellow">Kau membuatku sakit kepala, Nak.</font>

260
00:21:02,094 --> 00:21:05,305
<font color="yellow">Kenapa tak kau keluarkan?
Mungkin sakit kepalamu akan hilang.</font>

261
00:21:05,473 --> 00:21:08,224
<font color="yellow">Cobalah sedikit berpikir positif.</font>

262
00:21:08,392 --> 00:21:11,061
<font color="yellow">- Sial.
- Kuberitahu kau.</font>

263
00:21:11,228 --> 00:21:12,562
<font color="yellow">Kau lepaskan borgol ini...</font>

264
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:15,440
<font color="yellow">...dan aku akan menjadi
"Sammy Sunshine" yang positif bagimu.</font>

265
00:21:16,734 --> 00:21:21,112
<font color="yellow">Kau lihat gergaji yang ada
dalam tas peralatan di sana itu?</font>

266
00:21:22,657 --> 00:21:26,451
<font color="yellow">Ambilkan itu untukku?
Buat waktumu berarti.</font>

267
00:21:26,619 --> 00:21:28,203
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana menurutmu?
Ayolah.</font>

268
00:21:28,371 --> 00:21:30,121
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan aku dari benda ini.</font>

269
00:21:30,289 --> 00:21:32,332
<font color="yellow">Agar kau bisa memukuliku lagi?</font>

270
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,794
<font color="yellow">Atau menyebutku "negro" lagi?</font>

271
00:21:35,962 --> 00:21:38,296
<font color="yellow">Ayolah. Itu bukan
masalah pribadi.</font>

272
00:21:38,464 --> 00:21:41,299
<font color="yellow">Hanya saja kaummu dan kaumku
tak ditakdirkan untuk bercampur.</font>

273
00:21:41,467 --> 00:21:43,510
<font color="yellow">Itu saja.</font>

274
00:21:43,678 --> 00:21:46,304
<font color="yellow">Tak berarti kita tak bisa
bekerjasama...</font>

275
00:21:46,472 --> 00:21:49,557
<font color="yellow">...berbincang-bincang, selama
melibatkan keuntungan bersama.</font>

276
00:21:52,812 --> 00:21:56,106
<font color="yellow">Jadi, soal gergaji itu.</font>

277
00:21:56,273 --> 00:21:58,191
<font color="yellow">Kurasa kau juga ingin aku
ambilkan senapan di sana itu...</font>

278
00:21:58,359 --> 00:22:00,735
<font color="yellow">...agar kau bisa menembak polisi
itu saat dia kembali, 'kan?</font>

279
00:22:06,870 --> 00:22:14,833
<font color="yellow"><font color=#e>--- Penerjemah: Rizal Adam ---</font>
http://rizaladam.wordpress.com</font>

280
00:22:16,127 --> 00:22:19,337
<font color="yellow">Ya, kita menemukan saluran
gorong-gorong.</font>

281
00:22:19,505 --> 00:22:21,172
<font color="yellow">Jacqui benar.</font>

282
00:22:22,341 --> 00:22:23,967
<font color="yellow">Bisakah kita memotongnya?</font>

283
00:22:24,135 --> 00:22:26,845
<font color="yellow">Jika kita punya las potong
dan waktu setengah hari, tentu.</font>

284
00:22:27,013 --> 00:22:29,806
<font color="yellow">Gergaji Dale tentu saja
takkan berhasil.</font>

285
00:22:51,370 --> 00:22:52,954
<font color="yellow">Menemukan sesuatu yang
kau sukai?</font>

286
00:22:53,122 --> 00:22:56,541
<font color="yellow">Bukan aku, namun aku kenal
seseorang yang akan menyukainya.</font>

287
00:22:58,044 --> 00:23:00,045
<font color="yellow">Saudariku.</font>

288
00:23:00,212 --> 00:23:02,547
<font color="yellow">Dia masih seperti anak kecil
dalam beberapa hal.</font>

289
00:23:02,715 --> 00:23:04,466
<font color="yellow">Kuda bertanduk, naga...</font>

290
00:23:04,633 --> 00:23:06,301
<font color="yellow">...dia menyukai semua itu.</font>

291
00:23:06,469 --> 00:23:08,636
<font color="yellow">Tapi putri duyung adalah
segalanya.</font>

292
00:23:08,804 --> 00:23:11,389
<font color="yellow">Dia menyukai putri duyung.</font>

293
00:23:11,557 --> 00:23:13,141
<font color="yellow">Mengapa tak mengambilnya?</font>

294
00:23:14,393 --> 00:23:16,352
<font color="yellow">Ada seorang polisi menatapku.</font>

295
00:23:21,108 --> 00:23:23,068
<font color="yellow">Akankah ini dianggap
sebagai penjarahan?</font>

296
00:23:25,488 --> 00:23:28,573
<font color="yellow">Kurasa semua peraturan itu
tak berlaku lagi. Menurutmu?</font>

297
00:23:46,717 --> 00:23:48,718
<font color="yellow">- Kalian temukan apa di bawah?
- Bukan jalan keluar</font>

298
00:23:50,346 --> 00:23:53,556
<font color="yellow">Kita harus menemukan jalan
keluar segera.</font>

299
00:24:01,649 --> 00:24:04,734
<font color="yellow">Lokasi pembangunan itu, truk itu,
mereka selalu memiliki kunci.</font>

300
00:24:06,987 --> 00:24:09,155
<font color="yellow">Kita takkan pernah bisa
melewati para zombie itu.</font>

301
00:24:09,323 --> 00:24:10,573
<font color="yellow">Kau mengeluarkanku dari
tank itu.</font>

302
00:24:10,741 --> 00:24:13,118
<font color="yellow">Ya, namun mereka sedang makan.
Mereka teralihkan.</font>

303
00:24:13,285 --> 00:24:14,619
<font color="yellow">Kita bisa alihkan perhatian
mereka lagi?</font>

304
00:24:14,787 --> 00:24:16,996
<font color="yellow">Benar. Dengarkan dia.
Dia merencanakan sesuatu.</font>

305
00:24:17,164 --> 00:24:19,499
<font color="yellow">Sebuah pengalihan,
seperti di "Hogan's Heroes."</font>

306
00:24:19,667 --> 00:24:22,585
<font color="yellow">- Astaga. Hentikanlah.
- Mereka tertarik dengan suara, 'kan?</font>

307
00:24:22,753 --> 00:24:25,797
<font color="yellow">Benar, seperti anjing. Mereka
dengar suara, mereka akan datang.</font>

308
00:24:25,965 --> 00:24:27,674
<font color="yellow">- Apa lagi?
- Selain dari mereka mendengarmu?</font>

309
00:24:27,842 --> 00:24:30,426
<font color="yellow">Mereka melihatmu, membauimu dan jika
mereka menangkapmu, mereka memakanmu.</font>

310
00:24:30,594 --> 00:24:33,471
<font color="yellow">- Mereka bisa tahu kita dengan bau?
- Kau tak bisa?</font>

311
00:24:33,639 --> 00:24:36,266
<font color="yellow">Mereka berbau orang mati, kita
tidak. Itu cukup jelas.</font>

312
00:24:41,230 --> 00:24:42,939
<font color="yellow">Jika ada ide buruk
dilombakan di Olimpiade...</font>

313
00:24:43,107 --> 00:24:44,816
<font color="yellow">- ...ini akan meraih emas.
- Dia benar.</font>

314
00:24:44,984 --> 00:24:47,026
<font color="yellow">Hentikan saja. Butuh waktu
untuk memikirkan ini.</font>

315
00:24:47,194 --> 00:24:49,529
<font color="yellow">Berapa lama? Mereka sudah
menembus satu rangkai pintu.</font>

316
00:24:49,697 --> 00:24:51,197
<font color="yellow">Kaca itu takkan bertahan
selamanya.</font>

317
00:25:47,922 --> 00:25:49,839
<font color="yellow">Wayne Dunlap.</font>

318
00:25:50,007 --> 00:25:52,050
<font color="yellow">SIM Georgia.</font>

319
00:25:52,218 --> 00:25:56,221
<font color="yellow">Lahir di tahun 1979.</font>

320
00:26:00,726 --> 00:26:04,145
<font color="yellow">Dia memiliki 28 dolar
di sakunya saat dia meninggal...</font>

321
00:26:05,940 --> 00:26:07,941
<font color="yellow">...dan foto seorang gadis cantik.</font>

322
00:26:11,362 --> 00:26:14,656
<font color="yellow">"Salam sayang, dari Rachel."</font>

323
00:26:15,741 --> 00:26:17,033
<font color="yellow">Dia dulu seperti kita.</font>

324
00:26:17,201 --> 00:26:22,914
<font color="yellow">Mencemaskan tagihan, uang
sewa atau Super Bowl.</font>

325
00:26:25,376 --> 00:26:28,795
<font color="yellow">Jika kutemukan keluargaku,
akan kuceritakan soal Wayne.</font>

326
00:26:37,096 --> 00:26:39,180
<font color="yellow">Satu hal lagi...</font>

327
00:26:40,599 --> 00:26:42,767
<font color="yellow">Dia seorang donor organ.</font>

328
00:26:47,481 --> 00:26:49,105
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan!</font>

329
00:26:51,110 --> 00:26:53,653
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan.</font>

330
00:26:53,821 --> 00:26:55,196
<font color="yellow">Sial!</font>

331
00:26:55,364 --> 00:26:58,199
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan.</font>

332
00:26:59,228 --> 00:27:00,981
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan!</font>

333
00:27:01,412 --> 00:27:03,037
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan.</font>

334
00:27:16,510 --> 00:27:18,553
<font color="yellow">Terus memotong.</font>

335
00:27:21,849 --> 00:27:24,559
<font color="yellow">- Aku akan muntah.
- Nanti saja.</font>

336
00:27:38,866 --> 00:27:40,742
<font color="yellow">Semuanya sudah dapat
sarung tangan?</font>

337
00:27:42,703 --> 00:27:45,163
<font color="yellow">Jangan sampai kena kulit
atau masuk ke matamu.</font>

338
00:28:13,484 --> 00:28:15,318
<font color="yellow">Ya Tuhan!</font>

339
00:28:15,486 --> 00:28:18,363
<font color="yellow">Astaga.
Ini buruk.</font>

340
00:28:18,530 --> 00:28:19,989
<font color="yellow">Ini sungguh buruk.</font>

341
00:28:20,157 --> 00:28:21,491
<font color="yellow">Pikirkan hal yang lain.</font>

342
00:28:21,658 --> 00:28:23,076
<font color="yellow">Anak anjing dan anak kucing.</font>

343
00:28:23,243 --> 00:28:25,286
<font color="yellow">Anak anjing dan anak kucing
yang mati.</font>

344
00:28:28,791 --> 00:28:31,250
<font color="yellow">Ini jahat sekali.
Ada apa denganmu?</font>

345
00:28:31,418 --> 00:28:33,753
<font color="yellow">Lain kali biarkan dia dihajar.</font>

346
00:28:34,797 --> 00:28:37,340
<font color="yellow">- Maafkan aku.
- Kau payah!</font>

347
00:28:40,886 --> 00:28:44,055
<font color="yellow">- Kami tercium seperti mereka?
- Ya.</font>

348
00:28:45,557 --> 00:28:47,058
<font color="yellow">Glenn.</font>

349
00:28:49,061 --> 00:28:50,895
<font color="yellow">Sekedar jaga-jaga.</font>

350
00:28:58,654 --> 00:29:00,238
<font color="yellow">Jika kami berhasil kembali,
bersiaplah.</font>

351
00:29:00,406 --> 00:29:02,198
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana dengan Merle Dixon?</font>

352
00:29:15,170 --> 00:29:16,838
<font color="yellow">Berikan kapaknya.</font>

353
00:29:18,549 --> 00:29:21,801
<font color="yellow">- Kita butuh lebih banyak usus.
- Ya Tuhan!</font>

